          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Equity in Compensation Act</b></p> <p>This bill imposes an additional tax on the income of corporations that have gross revenues in excess of $1 billion and a wage disparity level in excess of 3,000%. A &quot;wage disparity level&quot; is defined as the ratio of the annual salary of the highest compensated officer of the corporation to the median annual salary of all employees of the corporation.</p>]]></text>
